a harmful task — approximates but does not perfectly capture every instance where a model refuses to help. </p><h2>Performance Benchmarks</h2><p>Finally, to validate that our method does not hurt general performance, we compared our models on the MMLU and HellaSwag benchmarks. Performance was generally similar: Our 70B LoRA model slightly outperforms the unchanged 70B Llama 2-Chat model—MMLU improves from 0.62 to 0.63 and HellaSwag from 0.82 to 0.83.</p><figure><img src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/bc9X7MbLueAfkGPqG-W21SyaljonFk8n0BhmzEBMy0w=/aHR0cHM6Ly9yZXMuY2xvdWRpbmFyeS5jb20vbGVzc3dyb25nLTItMC9pbWFnZS91cGxvYWQvZl9hdXRvLHFfYXV0by92MS9taXJyb3JlZEltYWdlcy9xbVFGSENnQ3lFRWp1eTVhNy9vdnE0c2drdWVwMXYyOXg0OWh5ag==" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/AVY85W3j5BG1vUIF3Xcps_cbtk7SG7Lk67GeIhYF7lI=/aHR0cHM6Ly9yZXMuY2xvdWRpbmFyeS5jb20vbGVzc3dyb25nLTItMC9pbWFnZS91cGxvYWQvZl9hdXRvLHFfYXV0by92MS9taXJyb3JlZEltYWdlcy9xbVFGSENnQ3lFRWp1eTVhNy9ocWRxdGVscnpkMHNpajd6dHJ0ZA== 140w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/dgq6Z7e7BthsGVkp7LIlkQjs7wJbz3bIryXkZvFZ6d8=/aHR0cHM6Ly9yZXMuY2xvdWRpbmFyeS5jb20vbGVzc3dyb25nLTItMC9pbWFnZS91cGxvYWQvZl9hdXRvLHFfYXV0by92MS9taXJyb3JlZEltYWdlcy9xbVFGSENnQ3lFRWp1eTVhNy91OWlranpjMW82eW44d3E5czVhcw== 220w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/Z77LnRYlPawPI2Q7z2PnZ2gy_xuNaPbdbCebnR2AtbA=/aHR0cHM6Ly9yZXMuY2xvdWRpbmFyeS5jb20vbGVzc3dyb25nLTItMC9pbWFnZS91cGxvYWQvZl9hdXRvLHFfYXV0by92MS9taXJyb3JlZEltYWdlcy9xbVFGSENnQ3lFRWp1eTVhNy91cjc0dnBkMmlwd3VpYWRhZ215aA== 300w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/VTvvOg-H71eP7cMLSYgScLzThFWMAEUa1KHrb3IuqnY=/aHR0cHM6Ly9yZXMuY2xvdWRpbmFyeS5jb20vbGVzc3dyb25nLTItMC9pbWFnZS91cGxvYWQvZl9hdXRvLHFfYXV0by92MS9taXJyb3JlZEltYWdlcy9xbVFGSENnQ3lFRWp1eTVhNy90cWxzd3hzdXVqeXV5a2d3bm5mdQ== 380w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/Z6NHWzT6Im6FkPJFJxXPguI1TbzveeeZJz-V-QCoN_M=/aHR0cHM6Ly9yZXMuY2xvdWRpbmFyeS5jb20vbGVzc3dyb25nLTItMC9pbWFnZS91cGxvYWQvZl9hdXRvLHFfYXV0by92MS9taXJyb3JlZEltYWdlcy9xbVFGSENnQ3lFRWp1eTVhNy9iajVsM2lwc2hzZHpieG10bGtzYw== 460